nodes.text: A male individual operated as a navigator in the Void Guides. The Void Guide served as the navigator aboard one of two Paccosh refugee starships fleeing the planet Rapacc. The Void Guide's vessel was stranded at the Paccosh rendezvous point when its hyperdrive failed, and eventually ran out of air. The Void Guide attempted to erase the ship's records before dying of asphyxiation.
